::DarkMouse::
She had given up on trying to impress Megatron so she just decided to give 
all the credit to Quickstrike and Scorponok for the things she did. She 
looked at Quickstrike for a moment and went back to looking at her notes.  
She closed her note book and walked closer to Quickstrike.
"If you would please commander help me with the lazar."

She walked out of the tunnel and to a large lazar driller that was in a far 
corner of the cave.  She drove it back to the end of the tunnel and stepped 
down from it.
"Your a bigger than I am and handling the controls may be easier for you.  
I'd like to watch the drilling up closer so I can make sure it is done 
according to my figures.  If it is not done just right, you could have the 
newly drilled tunnel collapse.  I just want to prevent that from happening. 
If that's OK with you commander?"
